OL,3,CSyrian refugees land cheese contract
OL,4,Cwith Aldi after TV show
OL,6,FRefugees who founded a cheese business
OL,7,Fin after fleeing war-torn Syria have
OL,8,Fwon a contract to get their product
OL,9,Fonto the shelves of one of the UK's
OL,10,Fbiggest supermarkets.
OL,12,FRazan Alsous and her husband Raghid
OL,13,FSandouk left Syria with their three
OL,14,Fchildren 12 years ago, before building
OL,15,Ftheir business Yorkshire Dama Cheese
OL,16,Fin from scratch.
