OL,3,CSyrian refugees land cheese contract
OL,4,Cwith Aldi after TV show
OL,6,FThe pair featured on Channel 4's
OL,7,FAldi's Next Big Thing ` where small
OL,8,Fbusinesses get to pitch to the
OL,9,Fsupermarket giant ` capturing the
OL,10,Fhearts of the judges after sharing how
OL,11,Fthey fled their home country in 2012.
OL,13,FThe presentation secured them a
OL,14,Fcontract to supply Aldi's 1,000 stores
OL,15,Fwith their Hello-Mi-Rolls, a Syrian-
OL,16,Fstyle cheese made using British cow
OL,17,Fand goat's milk.
