OL,6,FMs Alsous, who studied medicine and
OL,7,Fpharmacy, told of how she was inspired
OL,8,Fto start her successful enterprise
OL,9,Fafter she started searching for a job
OL,10,Fbut was unable to find one because of
OL,11,Fher lack of references and work
OL,12,Fhistory in the UK.
OL,14,FRazan Alsous, said: "It wasn't an easy
OL,15,Fjourney. We completely changed our
OL,16,Fprofessions when we came to the UK. We
OL,17,Falmost lost everything and had to
OL,18,Fsettle into a new life with three
OL,19,Fyoung children.
