OL,6,F"Eventually I thought, why not create
OL,7,Fa business and make Syrian cheese from
OL,8,Ffresh high-quality British milk? I had
OL,9,Fto use my scientific knowledge to make
OL,10,Fthe product. Without our background we
OL,11,Fwouldn't be able to deliver it."
OL,13,FThe entrepreneurs secured an order to
OL,14,Fsupply 40,000 Hello Mi Rolls, which
OL,15,Fare produced at their West Yorkshire
OL,16,Ffactory.
