OL,6,FJulie Ashfield, managing director of
OL,7,Fbuying at Aldi UK, said: "You can't
OL,8,Fhelp but fall in love with Razan and
OL,9,FRaghid. They're taking locally sourced
OL,10,Fproduce and making a wonderfully
OL,11,Finnovative product. I know it's going
OL,12,Fto sell."
OL,14,F"It wasn't easy at all to be honest,"
OL,15,FMs Alsous said.
OL,17,F"Julie is very honest and picky, and
OL,18,Fshe knows what she wants. I think they
OL,19,Ffound that the product is unique."
