OL,6,FRaghid Sandouk, added: "The milk, the
OL,7,Fcheese, the entire product is all made
OL,8,Fon our premises in Sowerby Bridge.
OL,9,FWhen we started it was just an idea to
OL,10,Fuse our Syrian cheese with local
OL,11,Fproducts on a small scale but now we
OL,12,Fhave this contract."
OL,14,FTheir products have also received a
OL,15,Froyal seal of approval in the past.
OL,17,FThe when she visited the factory in
OL,18,FSowerby Bridge.
